Today I presided over a meeting of the Council of Ministers, during which we decided to establish a national medical records base for all public and private hospital auditors. Http://t.co/ITIlT1RNCo
The unified national database will facilitate the transfer of patients between different hospitals and clinics and the ID number will be the standard number of the patient
We have also adopted an initiative to set up mobile health care units for older persons and citizens in remote areas to provide primary medical care and specialized care for them
We also adopted today the formation of a new board of directors of the National Information Council .. and change the organizational structure of the Council .. All the best for the new Council

We adopted the enactment of a law on the establishment of the Emirates Academy of Diplomacy to prepare specialized national cadres in this field in order to strengthen our distinguished international relations
The Council also approved today the final agreement with the European Union on the exemption of short-term residency visas (Schengen) for citizens of the state
